    <stitle>FRONT DRIVE AXLE WHEEL ENDS: ROCKWELL - CLEAN AND INSPECT - AXLE ASSEMBLIES</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>AXLE ASSEMBLIES</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">A completely assembled axle assembly can be steam cleaned on the outside to remove heavy
                amounts of dirt.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Before the axle is steam cleaned, close or put a cover over all openings in the axle
                assembly. Examples of openings are breathers or vents in air chambers.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
